Fireball" 10 5 80 The very first spell every mage learns. A large ball of flames erupts from your hand to engulf your enemy.
Lightning bolt" 15 10 85 You call down the forces of the storms to smite your foe. A flash of light blinds you momentarily as the lightning hits your enemy.
Shadow strike" 20 15 90 You conjure dark powers to assist you in defeating your enemy. A shadow-like figure appears and strikes your foe.
Earthquake" 30 25 100	The very earth responds to your call, trembling and cracking beneath the feet of your enemy, causing great damage.
Meteor fall" 50 50 70 You gather your strength and prepare the most devastating spell known to man. As you finish muttering the incantation a large, flaming meteor plummets towards your enemy.
